<!-- TITLE: Anything You Want cartoons -->
<!-- SUBTITLE: Philosophies on life and business, 7 chapters from my book, turned into short little animations. -->
<!-- MINUTES: 16 -->
<p>
Besides books, I'm a fan of movies, comic books, and animation. I love how the combination of visual and oral storytelling is so gripping.
</p><p>
So when I was releasing my own book in July 2011, I hired a great animator - Marvin Te from <a href="http://www.plainlysimplestudios.com/">http://www.plainlysimplestudios.com/</a> - and we worked together to make these 7 videos.
</p><p>
I hope to keep doing new videos like this for future essays, too. I really love the format.
</p><p>
If the videos are not showing, below, you can also see them at http://vimeo.com/album/1660848 or http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLCDDBA84EFA4061D1
</p>
